Merge pull request #7 from kloetzl/master

Fixed #5: strips whitespace from version string

release v2.0.2-1

This release des not change the source but fixes an issue with the build.

strips whitespace from version string

This fixes a build issue where the version string would contain a line break. Closes issue #5.
Update the project URL in CMakeLists.txt
Update to use renamed files in CMakeModules/ProjectCPack.cmake
Add Git revision check in VERSION.cmake
Remove SVN revision check in VERSION.cmake
Add markdown formatted files for github project pages
Fixed issue 4: Fixed version numbering in CMakeLists.txt.
Fixed issue 2: Added some cmake code to specify installation directories.

Major rewrite of libdivsufsort.
Added CPack support to create the source package.
Added OpenMP support for sssort.
The build system was changed to CMake. (http://www.cmake.org/)
